article_title: Two More Pieces Of Obamacare May Be On Their Way Out

article_metadata.author: Sally Pipes

og.description: Two bipartisan bills that would repeal parts of Obamacare will reach the House floor this week. They could blunt the damage Obamacare has done to our nation's economy and healthcare system. Lawmakers should pass them immediately.
